  # Get Analysis Job

  Retrieves the status and results of an analysis job.

  ## Path Parameter
  - `jobId`: The ID of the analysis job (from Create Analysis Job response)

  ## Response
  Returns the job status, analysis results (if completed), and metadata.

  ## Status Values
  - `PENDING`: Job is queued but not started
  - `SCRAPING`: Currently scraping the website
  - `ANALYZING`: Currently analyzing with Gemini
  - `COMPLETED`: Analysis complete, results available
  - `FAILED`: Analysis failed, check errorMessage

  ## Polling
  Poll this endpoint until status is `COMPLETED` or `FAILED`.
  Recommended: Poll every 2-5 seconds.
}
